<body class="fit rainbow">
  <!-- section 1 -->
  <div class="flex fit">
    <div class="section1-left-col">
      <h1 class="vertical-text dark-gray">THINK <span class="white">LEGACY</span> WITH US</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="section1-right-col">
      <div class="flex translation-l negative-margin-l">
        <h4>+ 771 221 7491</h4>
        <%= image_tag "star005.svg"%>
        <%= image_tag "star003.svg", class: "scale"%>
        <%= image_tag "star002.svg", class: "rotation"%>
        <%= image_tag "star004.svg", class: "scale"%>
        <%= image_tag "star005.svg", class: "rotation"%>
        <h4>Moonwalking Tours</h4>
        <%= image_tag "star005.svg"%>
        <%= image_tag "star003.svg", class: "scale"%>
        <%= image_tag "star002.svg", class: "rotation"%>
        <%= image_tag "star004.svg", class: "scale"%>
        <%= image_tag "star005.svg", class: "rotation"%>
        <h4>Book now!</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="flex translation-r negative-margin-r">
        <%= image_tag "icon004.svg"%>
        <%= image_tag "star004.svg"%>
        <%= image_tag "icon004.svg"%>
        <%= image_tag "star004.svg"%>
        <%= image_tag "icon004.svg"%>
      </div>
      <div class="flex translation-l negative-margin-l">
        <%= image_tag "icon001.svg"%>
        <h4><em>How to be a good ancestor?</em></h4>
        <%= image_tag "icon002.svg"%>
        <h4><em>Who existed before you?</em></h4>
        <%= image_tag "icon001.svg"%>
      </div>
      <div class="white-bg section1-content">
        <h3 class="gray">We are a <span class="border-bottom">local family</span> that would like to show you
        around our town in a unique way. Fed by several areas of knowledge and different approaches to reality,
        we will journey simultaneously through memory and through some of the most
        relevant issues of our times. Our tours are participatory, so not only do we invite you to explore our living
        spaces but your own inner worlds. You don't have to be or know anything in
        particular, just <span class="border-bottom">relax and enjoy.</span></h3>
      </div>
      <div class="section1-quote flex parent">
        <div class="circle-m white-bg translation-slow negative-margin-l"></div>
        <p class="child shine">Even a slight 1º change in perspective<br>can drastically affect the final trajectory</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- section 2 -->
  <h2 class="dark-gray">GUIDES</h2>
  <div class="flex">
    <div class="card flex-vertical">
      <div class="circle-sm white-bg"></div>
      <h3>Mariana Galán</h3>
      <h4>MA in Social Sculpture</h4>
      <p>imaginative<br>nonconformist<br>resourceful</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card flex-vertical">
      <div class="circle-sm white-bg"></div>
      <h3>Francisco Galán</h3>
      <h4>MA in Philosophy</h4>
      <p>razor-sharp logic<br>insightful<br>playful</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card flex-vertical">
      <div class="circle-sm white-bg"></div>
      <h3>Genevieve Galán</h3>
      <h4>PhD in History</h4>
      <p>witty<br>profound<br>welcoming</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- section 3 -->
  <div class="circle-sm white-bg translation-slow negative-margin-l"></div>
  <h2 class="dark-gray">TOURS</h2><br>
  <div class="tabs">
    <div class="tab">
      <input type="radio" name="tabgroup" id="tab-1" checked>
      <label for="tab-1">About Cars</label>
      <div class="content flex-top">
        <div class="section3-datetime">
          <h4>Sat & Sun<br>11:00<br>13:00</h4><br>
          <h4>30 min</h4>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p>According to the Dutch company TomTom, in 2017 Mexico City occupied
          -for a second consecutive year- the first position in their international
          traffic congestion index. Since the situation is not going away for many
          other urban areas worldwide, our complex city is a pivotal place to reflect
          on the benefits and increasing problems that cars bring to our contemporary
          life. <br><br> From state-of-the-art engineering creations to worrisome air
          pollution levels in the world, this walking tour is a concise and brief
          opportunity to use your experience and consider the past, present, and
          future of our living spaces. <br><br> This tour was successfully first introduced
          at Oxford in 2018 as part of the MA in Social Sculpture in collaboration
          with the University of the Trees.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section3-datetime">

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tab">
      <input type="radio" name="tabgroup" id="tab-2">
      <label for="tab-2">Moral dilemmas</label>
      <div class="content">
        <h4>1 hr 30 min</h4>
        <p>Have you ever wondered who existed before you and how they lived, felt
        and thought? Are we what they dreamed the world would be like? How will
        our daily lives impact future generations? Is reality something fixed or
        something that we can change? <br><br> Our life is full of choices. This
        experience is one of our most beloved original creations: it allows you
        to play while you work out your decision-making skills. Shape your own
        tour as you gradually walk through the scenarios we present you.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tab">
      <input type="radio" name="tabgroup" id="tab-3">
      <label for="tab-3">Abandoned spaces</label>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Every present is condemed to ruins. Explore the ruins of other futures
        in this past-futures experience around some forgotten pieces of La colonia
      Roma.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%= image_tag "icon003.svg"%>
</body>
